      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "K"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      74                   to   v-pos                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
