      *              * conda se interlinea di separazione richiesta o  *
      *              * no                                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-snx-sep           =    "S"
                     move  2              to   w-stp-ctr-lin-res
           else      move  1              to   w-stp-ctr-lin-res      .
           if        p-res                >    w-stp-ctr-lin-res
                     go to stp-rig-det-200.
       stp-rig-det-100.
